From Brian Cherkauer Subject Re IIvx Upgrade Question In article jas Jeff Sullivan writes If you get teh IIvx upgrade does it include a new sticker to cover the IIvx identifier with a Centris indetifier I can't say for sure with the IIvx upgrade but I wondered the same thing when I ordered my LC LC III Turns out the upgrade is actually an entire CPU minus any disk You pull the floppy and hard drives out of the old one stick them in the new one and you've got an LC The IIvx may be the same It might be something to look into for those people who are unhappy that Apple only sells Macs pre packaged with the Of course the price is quite a bit higher without the trade Brian